com.opengamma.strata.product

Interface LegalEntity


  • public interface LegalEntity
    A legal entity.

    A legal entity is one of the building blocks of finance, representing an organization. It is used to capture details for credit worthiness. The legal entity can be looked up in ReferenceData using the identifier.

    Implementations of this interface must be immutable beans.
